    • Constructor Detail

      • OptimizationResult

        public OptimizationResult(java.io.File optimizedFile,
                  long optimizedFileSize,
                  java.io.File originalFile,
                  long originalFileSize,
                  boolean fileTypeChanged,
                  boolean failedAutomatedTest,
                  boolean isBrowserSpecific)
        Constructor which sets all of the values.
        Parameters:
        optimizedFile - The optimized version of the image
        optimizedFileSize - The size of the optimized image (aka File.length()
        originalFile - The original version of the image
        originalFileSize - The size of the original image (aka File.length()
        fileTypeChanged - true if the file type of the optimized image is different than the file type of the original images. This usually is true when converting a GIF to PNG because it is small in length.
        failedAutomatedTest - true if the file failed the automated validation after compression and should be considered ineligible for check-in. If false then we have a valid optimized image.
        isBrowserSpecific - true if the image format only works in one type of browser.
